Source: Sxlaris
Wondrous Item, Uncommon
___
A short club with a hollowed out barrel, the end of which is blackened with soot. When you swing the weapon, a cascade of magical sparks springs forth from the end of the barrel, hitting whatever is in melee range of you.

When you attack with this weapon, it does 2d4 - 4 fire damage for a minimum of 1. For each 4 you rolled, roll an additional 2d4 and add it to the total damage. For every additional 4 you roll with this ability, add another 2d4. 
